{
  "stem": "14190.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I usually was a very good girl and listened, you know, very conform to what I needed to do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That one particular day that looked such a nice day early in the morning, we were very early up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were up 6 o'clock, because there was like a mass in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had like a little chapel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they went to mass.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took-- took us there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my sister was not very often there, because she wouldn't sit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I-- they took me almost every time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, after-- after the mass, we would go and have a breakfast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after the breakfast, it was a quiet time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So during that quiet time, which was still very early, I ventured.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't remember that I wasn't supposed to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I-- you know, I ventured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the forest was like not-- I mean, right there, very close by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went into the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then I went a little bit farther.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you know, very curious, wasn't frightened at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I didn't have to go very far from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I-- I started to hear these noises, these noises, pah, pah, pah, pah, pah, pah, pah, like this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So wherever I heard this, I-- I-- followed that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it wasn't really that-- that far.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- I stand behind a-- behind a tree.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I see this group of people undressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
